Privacy Policy
Last updated: October 25, 2013
WangWangGo Studio, respects the privacy rights of our users and are committed to protecting the information collected through its online products, online services and websites including, but not limited to WangWangGo Studio's games (together “Services”). WangWangGo Studio has adopted this privacy policy (“Privacy Policy”) to explain how WangWangGo Studio collects, stores, and uses the information collected in connection with WangWangGo Studio’ Services.
BY INSTALLING, USING, REGISTERING TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESSING THE SERVICES, YOU AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY AND GIVE AN EXPLICIT AND INFORMED CONSENT TO THE PROCESSING OF YOUR PERSONAL DATA IN ACCORDANCE WITH THIS PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY, PLEASE DO NOT INSTALL, USE, REGISTER TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESS THE SERVICES.
WangWangGo Studio reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at reasonable times, so please review it frequently. If WangWangGo Studio makes material or significant changes to this Privacy Policy, WangWangGo Studio may post a notice on WangWangGo Studio's website along with the updated Privacy Policy. Your continued use of Services will signify your acceptance of the changes to this Privacy Policy.
We access and use:
Non-personal data using tools or third party analytical software that does not directly enable WangWangGo Studio to identify you. The types of non-personal data WangWangGo Studio may collect and use include, but are not limited to: (i) device properties; (ii) device software platform and firmware; (iii) mobile phone carrier; (iv) geographical data such as zip code, area code and location; (v) game score and achievements; (vi) other non-personal data as reasonably required by WangWangGo Studio to enhance the Services and other WangWangGo Studio products and services.
Sharing:
WangWangGo Studio collects and processes personal data on a voluntary basis and it is not in the business of selling your personal data to third parties. We will not share any personally identifiable information about you to with third parties. WangWangGo Studio does reserve the right, to share non-personal information with third parties
WangWangGo Studio may hire agents and contractors to collect and process personal data on WangWangGo Studio's behalf and in such cases such agents and contractors will be instructed to comply with our Privacy Policy and to use personal data only for the purposes for which the third party has been engaged by WangWangGo Studio. These agents and contractors may not use your personal data for their own marketing purposes. WangWangGo Studio may use third party service providers such as credit card processors, e-mail service providers, shipping agents, data analyzers and business intelligence providers. WangWangGo Studio has the right to share your personal data as necessary for the aforementioned third parties to provide their services for WangWangGo Studio. WangWangGo Studio is not liable for the acts and omissions of these third parties, except as provided by mandatory law.
WangWangGo Studio may disclose your personal data to third parties as required by law enforcement or other government officials in connection with an investigation of fraud, intellectual property infringements, or other activity that is illegal or may expose you or WangWangGo Studio to legal liability. WangWangGo Studio may also disclose your personal data to third parties when WangWangGo Studio has a reason to believe that a disclosure is necessary to address potential or actual injury or interference with WangWangGo Studio's rights, property, operations, users or others who may be harmed or may suffer loss or damage, or WangWangGo Studio believes that such disclosure is necessary to protect WangWangGo Studio's rights, combat fraud and/or comply with a judicial proceeding, court order, or legal process served on WangWangGo Studio.